    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Compound that is a salt with the sulfate ion SO4 2-, or an ester of sulfuric acid. Sulfates comprise an enormous group of chemicals that contain the element sulfur. Sulfates are used in a variety of common products and processes. </Note_Text>
